    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model demonstrates adequate credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions under the nominal COU operating envelope. RH < 0.85 at all five operating points satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The assessment team notes that all validation evidence derives from nominal hardware operating under controlled laboratory conditions, consistent with standard practice for MRL 2 Class II device submissions.",
